Customer surveys
We do this by comparing normal consumption values (typically at your power meter) to car charger grid consumptions. The data used to do this is the registration date of the car, the car registration address and the type of electrical vehicle. This allows us to better calculate loads in the grid and better allow us to plan for maintenance and grid development requirements.
E.ON Privacy Policy
When you log in to the eon.se and in the E.ON app "Mitt E.ON", login information is processed together with an anonymized user-id for our analysis of the use of our services. We then use Google Analytics. This only happens if you agree to this, which you do at eon.se and in the E.ON app. It is therefore entirely voluntary to do so.
