Categories of personal data that we process are customer information, purchase information, technical information, service information and demographic information. Examples of data within these categories are how long you have been a customer, consumption or choice of products. Examples of situations where profiling is used are marketing, needs-adapted offers, development of products and services, statistics and analysis, newsletters and other information mailings. Personal data can thus be disclosed to and collected from partners and authorities. The information and offers made within the framework of profiling are available to all customers if desired.
