Environmental
In our Responsible Procurement Policy, we set general environmental requirements for suppliers. By signing the policy, the supplier commits to comply with these requirements. To ensure that particularly hazardous substances are not used, we have identified chemicals / substances that are banned for used within E.ON. The ban on the use of these products also applies to our suppliers / contractors. Furthermore, we also set requirements for raw materials, production, transport and the use of chemicals.
