The ongoing pandemic is currently at a stage where society has been able to open up and recommendations and restrictions have been removed or reduced. We continuously monitor developments and follow current recommendations from the Public Health Agency in Sweden and Danish Health Authority to continue to protect our employees and to ensure that we can conduct our important and socially critical business.
